      <title>加州大学因抵制以色列而遭到强烈反对</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/california-university-sees-backlash-over-israel-academic-boycott</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州公立文理学院索诺玛州立大学校长在宣布与亲巴勒斯坦抗议者达成一项有争议的协议一天后被停职，该协议包括对以色列的学术抵制以及学生活动人士执行该协议的作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/california-university-sees-backlash-over-israel-academic-boycott</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 20:03:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织批准使用特别提款权为气候和社会项目融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/imf-approves-using-sdrs-as-hybrid-capital-for-multilateral-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织批准了各国将储备资产引导至多边开发银行的新方式，这是为应对气候适应和减贫等挑战筹集资金的更广泛努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/imf-approves-using-sdrs-as-hybrid-capital-for-multilateral-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 16:07:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，国库控股和公积金正在考虑将马来西亚机场私有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/khazanah-epf-are-said-to-weigh-taking-malaysia-airports-private</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚机场控股有限公司 (Malaysian Airports Holdings Bhd.) 即将被私有化，其两大股东联手收购公司 Global Infrastructure Partners 和阿布扎比投资局 (Abu Dhabi Investment Authority) 向机场运营商提出收购要约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/khazanah-epf-are-said-to-weigh-taking-malaysia-airports-private</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 03:32:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
